import { FC } from 'react';
import { Stack, Divider, Link, Box, Card, Button } from '@mui/material';


const NavBar: FC = () => {



  return (
    <Card>
      <Stack width='100%' direction="row" spacing={2} sx={{ px: 4, py: 2 }} bgcolor='purple'>
       <Link href='#' underline="none">
         Resume/CV
      </Link>
      <Divider orientation="vertical" flexItem/>
      <Link href='#' underline="none" target="_blank">
         Github
        </Link>
        <Divider orientation="vertical" flexItem/>
        <Link href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/webb-charles/' underline="none" target="_blank">
         LinkedIn
        </Link>
      <Divider orientation="vertical" flexItem/>
       <Button

       >Photos</Button>
      <Divider orientation="vertical" flexItem/>
       <Box> Contact form </Box>
     </Stack>
    </Card>
  )
}

export default NavBar;
